OL,3,CGovernment condemns 'politically
OL,4,Cmotivated' prosecution of Jimmy Lai
OL,6,FThe UK government has condemned the
OL,7,F"politically motivated prosecution" of
OL,8,Fa Hong Kong media tycoon and British
OL,9,Fnational.
OL,11,FJimmy Lai, 78, has been found guilty
OL,12,Fby a Hong Kong court of conspiracy and
OL,13,Fsedition charges under the territory's
OL,14,FBeijing-imposed national security law.
OL,16,FMr Lai, a pro-democracy activist who
OL,17,Ffounded the now-defunct Hong Kong
OL,18,Fnewspaper Apple Daily, has been a
OL,19,Fpersistent critic of the Chinese
OL,20,Fgovernment.
