OL,3,CGovernment condemns 'politically
OL,4,Cmotivated' prosecution of Jimmy Lai
OL,6,FHe was arrested in 2020 under the
OL,7,Fnational security law, which was
OL,8,Fbrought in after anti-government
OL,9,Fprotests the previous year.
OL,11,FMr Lai, who has spent much of the time
OL,12,Fsince in solitary confinement, pleaded
OL,13,Fnot guilty to all the charges brought
OL,14,Fagainst him.
OL,16,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,17,Fcriticised the verdict by the Hong
OL,18,FKong court, saying: "The UK condemns
OL,19,Fthe politically motivated prosecution
OL,20,Fof Jimmy Lai that has resulted in
OL,21,Ftoday's guilty verdict.
