OL,3,CGovernment condemns 'politically
OL,4,Cmotivated' prosecution of Jimmy Lai
OL,6,F"Jimmy Lai has been targeted by the
OL,7,FChinese and Hong Kong governments for
OL,8,Fpeacefully exercising his right to
OL,9,Ffreedom of expression.
OL,11,F"Beijing's national security law was
OL,12,Fimposed on Hong Kong to silence
OL,13,FChina's critics.
OL,15,F"The UK has repeatedly called for the
OL,16,Fnational security law to be repealed
OL,17,Fand for an end to the prosecution of
OL,18,Fall individuals charged under it.
