OL,3,CGovernment condemns 'politically
OL,4,Cmotivated' prosecution of Jimmy Lai
OL,6,F"We continue to call for Mr Lai's
OL,7,Fimmediate release, for all necessary
OL,8,Ftreatment and for full access to
OL,9,Findependent medical professionals."
OL,11,FDame Priti Patel, shadow foreign
OL,12,Fsecretary, described Mr Lai's case as
OL,13,Fa "political show trial" which was "an
OL,14,Foutrage to democracy, personal freedom
OL,15,Fand liberty".
OL,17,FShe added: "His degrading treatment
OL,18,Fand imprisonment at the hands of the
OL,19,FChinese Communist Party's
OL,20,Fauthoritarian regime has been
OL,21,Fappalling."
