OL,6,FDame Priti urged Prime Minister Sir
OL,7,FKeir Starmer to "directly raise
OL,8,FJimmy's case with President Xi
OL,9,F(Jinping) and demand Jimmy's immediate
OL,10,Frelease from custody so his ordeal can
OL,11,Fend, he can be returned to Britain and
OL,12,Fbe reunited with his family".
OL,14,FA cross-party group of MPs criticised
OL,15,Fthe government for not having taken
OL,16,Fstronger action ahead of Mr Lai's
OL,17,Fconviction.
