OL,3,CGovernment condemns 'politically
OL,4,Cmotivated' prosecution of Jimmy Lai
OL,6,F"While other countries such as the
OL,7,FUnited States, Canada and Australia
OL,8,Fhave secured the release of their
OL,9,Fnationals from arbitrary detention in
OL,10,FChina and Hong Kong, the UK has failed
OL,11,Fto do so despite the unique
OL,12,Frelationship between the UK and Hong
OL,13,FKong enshrined in international
OL,14,Fobligations in the Basic Law.
OL,16,F"If the UK had taken faster, firmer
OL,17,Fand more fervent action to secure his
OL,18,Frelease Jimmy Lai could be spending
OL,19,FChristmas with his family where he
OL,20,Fbelongs, rather than arbitrarily
OL,21,Fdetained in Hong Kong."
